{"tid":429243,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"痴身真係好攰","createTime":"2017-10-08T16:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T17:45:00.000Z","uid":101759,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"314ac468b3d0d2e816344154e032591f4fea5ffd","tid":429243,"uid":101759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"我認自己都係比較痴身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男朋友依家讀書又返緊intern<br />\n佢出街成日都話攰<br />\n我都盡量去佢屋企附近揾佢<br />\n自己都比當初獨立左好多<br />\n但佢好似都想多啲私人空間做下自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明佢返工讀書辛苦<br />\n但我都覺得好唔開心 遲啲佢正式返工係咪更加唔使見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f6c1c572b63aa0ed6b2ca322804282284e7cdf","tid":429243,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"攤出嚟傾"},{"pid":"ed175c2720958bc9d57de88916d1697ce009f91f","tid":429243,"uid":101759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攤出嚟傾</blockquote><br />\n佢之前都有就我<br />\n但好似本身講好得閒一齊溫書 <br />\n我都無要求再去邊度玩<br />\n佢突然又話自己溫書有效率啲<br />\n又話之後越黎越忙 會越黎越少時間見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca874e7ae070040a3e76e51125ad35ea59e30a71","tid":429243,"uid":140696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"太痴身好煩架<br />\n體諒下你男朋友啦"},{"pid":"2c1444081d80c76cfcf57c6e1d79702b75418a5b","tid":429243,"uid":84412,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T17:45:00.000Z","msg":"係珍惜既幾攰都會抽時間見"}]}